726299f-a.title: Queens: Calamus Avenue - 71st Street
726299f-a.text:
Calamus Ave., at the S.E. corner of 71st Street, showing in a set of two views the rear of the M. Pinkney house as viewed northeastward.
May 28, 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

726300f-b.title: Queens: Calamus Avenue - 71st Street
726300f-b.text:
Calamus Ave., south side, east from 71st Street, showing at the right the M. Pinkney house which was in the family from 1860 to 1891. One Howard owned it in 1910. This is a set of four views.
April 1925.
Views 1 and 2.
View 3: March 1923.
View 4: March 1923 .
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
